translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,146,Abo Sibanike isiBhalo bayamazi yena (uMuhammad) kanye njengoko besazi oonyana babo. Kodwa iqela elithile kubo liyayifihla inyaniso ngoku liyazi
  2,147,Le yinyaniso evela eNkosini yakho ke ngoko musa ukuba ngomnye wabo bathandabuzayo
  2,148,"Kuba nasiphi na isizwe sinecala esijongisa kulo (xa sithandazayo), ke ngoko khawulezisani ukwenza konke okulungileyo. Nokuba niphi na apho nikhoyo. UAllâh Uya Kunidibanisa ndawonye nonke (ngoMhla wokuGqibela). Inene uAllâh Unamandla okwenza izinto zonke"
  2,149,Nokuba niphi na apho nikhoyo xa niza kuthandaza jongisani ubuso benu ngakwicala leMasjid eNgcwele (eMakkah). Leyo yinyaniso evela eNkosini yakho. UAllâh Ayingaba Akakwazi oko nikwenzayo
  2,150,"Naphi na apho nikhoyo (xa) niqalisa ukuthandaza, jongisani ubuso benu kwicala leMasjid eNgcwele, kananjalo nokuba sele niphi na, bhekisani ubuso benu ngakuyo, ukuze nabantu bangenzi ngxoxo nani ngaphandle kwabo bazizingcoli phakathi kwabo, ningankwantyiswa ngabo ke nina koko yoyikani Mna! Ukuze Ndifezekise uBabalo lwaM kuni, khona ukuze nikhokeleleke"
  2,151,"Kananjalo Sithume uMthunywa kuni ongowenu ecengceleza iiVesi zeThu (ze’Kur`ân), enihlambulula, enifundisa isiBhalo (i’Kur`ân) nobulumko, enifundisa noko benikade ningakwazi"
  2,152,"Ke kaloku (Hlalani) niNdikhumbula (naM) Ndiya (kuhlala) Ndinikhumbula, yibani nombulelo kuM ningaze nibe ngabangakholwayo kuM"
  2,153,Ke nina bakholwayo! Funani uncedo ngomonde nangeSalâh inene uAllâh Unabo banomonde